---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Eazy.Family is built by parents, for families. Learn about our mission to bring families closer through thoughtful, private technology.">

  <div style="position: fixed; top: -10rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.15; background: radial-gradient(circle, hsl(270 88% 55%), transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; z-index: -1;"></div>

  <div style="max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 8rem 1.25rem 4rem;">

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section style="text-align: center; max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto 5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 5vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <span class="grad-text">Built by parents,<br />for families</span>
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        Eazy.Family started with a simple frustration: modern families are more connected than ever, yet coordination still happens across five different apps, group chats, and sticky notes. We built the app we wished existed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Our values</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
        {[
          { icon: "❤️", t: "Family first", b: "Every product decision starts with one question: does this make family life easier or more joyful?" },
          { icon: "🔒", t: "Radical privacy", b: "No ads. No data brokers. No selling your family's information. Your data belongs to you." },
          { icon: "👥", t: "Inclusive by design", b: "Grandparents, teenagers, expats — Eazy.Family works for every family member in their preferred language." },
          { icon: "⚡", t: "Thoughtful AI", b: "AI that helps without intruding. Our assistant handles the busywork so you can focus on the people that matter." },
        ].map(v => (
          <div class="card" style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
            <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0;">{v.icon}</div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">{v.t}</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">{v.b}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story -->
    <section style="max-width: 40rem; margin: 0 auto 5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our story</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        Eazy.Family was founded in Zurich, Switzerland — a city of multilingual families navigating busy lives. We saw firsthand how international families struggled to stay organized across language barriers, time zones, and the chaos of modern parenthood.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        We believe technology should bring families closer, not add more noise. That's why Eazy.Family is private-first, beautifully simple, and works in the language your family actually speaks — whether that's German, French, Italian, or English.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="card" style="text-align: center; border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 3rem 2rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Join our family</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Start for free. No credit card required.</p>
      <a href="https://app.eazy.family/onboarding" class="btn-primary">Get Started Free</a>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
